                     <interp inst="t18760918-403-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="embezzlement"></interp>, Embezzling the sums of 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 9<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 7 1/2 <hi rend="italic">d</hi>., 21<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., and 3<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 14<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., received on account of <persName id="t18760918-name-102" type="victimName">
